\c 34
\s UJeremiya uxwayisa uZedekhiya
\p
\v 1 Ilizwi elafika kuJeremiya livela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, lapho uNebhukadinezari inkosi yeBhabhiloni,\x + 39.1; 52.4. 2 Kho. 25.1.\x* lebutho lakhe lonke, lemibuso yonke yomhlaba yokubusa kwesandla sakhe,\x + 1.15; 51.28.\x* lazo zonke izizwe, babesilwa bemelene leJerusalema bemelene layo yonke imizi yayo, lisithi:
\v 2 Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli: Hamba ukhulume kuZedekhiya inkosi yakoJuda\x + 39.1; 52.4. 2 Kho. 25.1.\x* uthi kuye: Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Khangela, nginikela lumuzi esandleni senkosi yeBhabhiloni,\x + 21.10; 32.3.\x* ukuthi iwutshise ngomlilo.\x + 21.10; 34.22.\x*
\v 3 Lawe kawuyikuphunyuka esandleni sayo,\x + 32.4.\x* kodwa uzabanjwa isibili, unikelwe esandleni sayo;\x + 32.4.\x* lamehlo akho azabona amehlo enkosi yeBhabhiloni,\x + 32.4.\x* lomlomo wayo uzakhuluma lomlomo wakho;\x + 32.4.\x* njalo uzakuya eBhabhiloni.\x + 32.5.\x*
\v 4 Kodwa zwana ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd*, Zedekhiya, nkosi yakoJuda:\x + 38.17,20.\x* Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* ngawe: Kawuyikufa ngenkemba.
\v 5 Uzakufa ngokuthula,\x + 38.17,20.\x* lanjengokubaselwa kwaboyihlo,\x + 2 Lan. 21.19. 1 Sam. 31.12.\x* amakhosi endulo, ayephambi kwakho, ngokunjalo bazakubasela, bakulilele,\x + 22.18.\x* \add besithi\add*: Maye inkosi! Ngoba mina ngilikhulumile lelolizwi, itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*.
\v 6 UJeremiya umprofethi wasewakhuluma wonke lamazwi kuZedekhiya inkosi yakoJuda eJerusalema,
\v 7 lapho ibutho lenkosi yeBhabhiloni lisilwa limelene leJerusalema limelene layo yonke imizi yakoJuda eyayisele, limelene leLakishi\x + Josh. 10.3.\x* limelene leAzeka;\x + Josh. 10.10.\x* ngoba yiyo imizi ebiyelweyo eyayisisele phakathi kwemizi yakoJuda.\x + 2 Kho. 18.13,14. 2 Lan. 11.5,9.\x*\x + 4.5.\x*
\s Mayelana lezigqili ezazingakhululwanga
\p
\v 8 Ilizwi elafika kuJeremiya livela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, emva kokuthi inkosi uZedekhiya esenzile isivumelwano labo bonke abantu ababeseJerusalema ukumemezela inkululeko kubo,\x + 34.15,17. Levi 25.10.\x*
\v 9 ukuthi ngulowo lalowo ayekele isigqili sakhe\x + Levi 25.39,40,41,42,43,44,45,46.\x* sihambe sikhululekile,\x + Isa. 58.6.\x* langulowo lalowo isigqilikazi sakhe, umHebheru kumbe umHebherukazi, ukuze kungabi khona umuntu owenza umJuda engumfowabo abe yisigqili.\x + Neh. 5.8,9,10,11,12.\x*
\v 10 Kwasekulalela zonke iziphathamandla labo bonke abantu ababengene lesosivumelwano sokuthi ngulowo lalowo ayekele isigqili sakhe langulowo lalowo isigqilikazi sakhe sihambe sikhululekile,\x + Isa. 58.6.\x* bangaphindi bazenze zibe yizigqili; basebelalela, ba\add zi\add*yekela \add za\add*hamba.
\v 11 Kodwa emva kwalokho baphenduka,\x + 34.21.\x* bazibuyisa izigqili lezigqilikazi ababeziyekele zihambe zikhululekile,\x + Isa. 58.6.\x* bazehlisela phansi zaba yizigqili lezigqilikazi.
\p
\v 12 Ngakho ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* lafika kuJeremiya livela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni, lisithi:\x + Gen. 19.24.\x*
\v 13 Itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli: Mina ngenza isivumelwano laboyihlo mhla ngibakhupha elizweni leGibhithe,\x + Eks. 20.2.\x* endlini yobugqili, ngisithi:
\v 14 Ekupheleni\x + Dute. 14.28; 26.12.\x* kweminyaka eyisikhombisa lizayekela ahambe, ngulowo lalowo umfowabo umHebheru\x + Eks. 21.2.\x*\x + Dute. 15.12.\x* owayethengiswe kuwe,\x + Dute. 15.12.\x* esekusebenzele iminyaka eyisithupha, umyekele ahambe ekhululekile esuka kuwe. Kodwa oyihlo kabangilalelanga,\x + 7.24,26; 11.8; 17.23; 25.4; 35.15; 44.5.\x* kababekanga indlebe yabo.\x + 7.24,26; 11.8; 17.23; 25.4; 35.15; 44.5.\x*
\v 15 Lina seliphendukile lamuhla, lenza okulungileyo emehlweni ami, limemezela inkululeko, ngulowo lalowo kumakhelwane wakhe,\x + 34.15,17. Levi 25.10.\x* lenza isivumelwano phambi kwami endlini ebizwa ngebizo lami.\x + 34.8. 2 Kho. 23.3. Neh. 10.29.\x*
\v 16 Kodwa liphendukile, langcolisa ibizo lami,\x + Levi 18.21; 19.12.\x* libuyisa, ngulowo lalowo isigqili sakhe langulowo lalowo isigqilikazi sakhe,\x + 34.11.\x* ebeliziyekele zahamba zikhululekile njengokufisa kwazo,\x + 2.24.\x* lazehlisela phansi, zaba yizigqili lezigqilikazi zenu.
\v 17 Ngakho itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*: Lina kalingilalelanga, ukumemezela inkululeko,\x + 34.15,17. Levi 25.10.\x* kube ngulowo lalowo kumfowabo langulowo lalowo kumakhelwane wakhe; khangelani, ngizamemezela kini,\x + Mat. 7.2. Gal. 6.7. Jak. 2.13.\x* itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*, inkululeko\x + Levi 25.42,55.\x* enkembeni,\x + 14.12.\x* kumatshayabhuqe wesifo,\x + 14.12.\x* lendlaleni;\x + 14.12.\x* ngilinikele libe yisesabiso\x + 24.9.\x* kuyo yonke imibuso yomhlaba.\x + 29.18.\x*
\v 18 Nginikele amadoda aseqileyo isivumelwano sami, angaqinisanga amazwi esivumelwano asenza phambi kwami,\x + 34.8.\x* lapho adabula ithole kabili,\x + Gen. 15.10.\x* adlula phakathi kweziqa zalo;
\v 19 iziphathamandla zakoJuda, leziphathamandla zeJerusalema, abathenwa,\x + 29.2.\x* labapristi, labo bonke abantu belizwe, abadabula phakathi\x + Gen. 15.10.\x* kweziqa zethole.
\v 20 Yebo, ngizabanikela esandleni sezitha zabo lesandleni salabo abadinga impilo yabo;\x + 22.25.\x* lezidumbu zabo zizakuba yikudla kwenyoni zamazulu lenyamazana zomhlaba.\x + 7.33; 16.4; 19.7. Hez. 29.5. Dute. 28.26.\x*
\v 21 LoZedekhiya inkosi yakoJuda leziphathamandla zakhe ngizabanikela esandleni sezitha zabo, lesandleni salabo abadinga impilo yabo,\x + 22.25.\x* lesandleni sebutho lenkosi yeBhabhiloni, abenyuke basuka kini.\x + 34.11; 37.5,11.\x*
\v 22 Khangelani, ngizalaya,\x + Isa. 10.6.\x* itsho iN\nd kosi\nd*, ngibabuyise kulumuzi;\x + 37.8.\x* njalo bazakulwa bemelene lawo,\x + 37.8.\x* bawuthumbe,\x + 37.8.\x*\x + 32.3; 38.3.\x* bawutshise ngomlilo;\x + 37.8.\x*\x + 34.2.\x* lemizi yakoJuda ngizayenza \add ibe\add* lunxiwa\x + 9.11.\x* olungelamhlali.\x + 4.7.\x*